text: 16|119|banteabmk pitabrakd nasa  mcheasa robsa anakchea anak  aphytosa champoh puok del ban sang ampeuaeakrak daoy pheap lngong khlaw  kraoyomk puokke ban sarphap tosakamhosa  ning ban kekhluon  vinh .  pitabrakd nasa  mcheasa robsa anak mha aphytosa mha  anet sraleanh banteabpi kar sarphap kamhosa noh .
